University of Michigan, Ann Arbor, MI\\
\textit{Ongoing Ph.D. research supervised by Professor Susan Murphy}
\begin{itemize}
\item Cleaned and formatted data from HeartSteps, a micro-randomized trial of smartphone interventions designed to users' physical activity.
\item Analyzed HeartSteps data using novel methodology for estimating time-varying causal effects.
\end{itemize}
